OL,5,Cregister
OL,7,FPressure has been put on Guernsey
OL,8,Fpoliticians to introduce a public sex
OL,9,Foffenders register on the island.
OL,11,FA letter has been sent to all deputies
OL,12,Farguing that a fully public register
OL,13,Fwould help protect the community.
OL,15,FThis would take it beyond legislation
OL,16,Fin both Jersey and the UK, where
OL,17,Fparents, carers and teachers can
OL,18,Fformally ask the police if they have
OL,19,Fsuspicions about someone.
