OL,7,FJane, whose name has also been
OL,8,Fchanged, was assaulted when she was a
OL,9,Fchild.
OL,11,FShe says: "Places where he has worked,
OL,12,Fwhere I don't think he should be
OL,13,Fworking. I approached his boss and
OL,14,Fexplained the situation... I don't
OL,15,Fthink he was in that job much longer."
OL,17,FSarah's Law, in memory of murdered
OL,18,Fschool girl Sarah Payne, already
OL,19,Fallows parents, carers and guardians
OL,20,Fto find out about suspected child sex
OL,21,Fabusers in the UK and Jersey.
