OL,7,FWhat these victims in Guernsey are
OL,8,Fcalling for is a fully public register
OL,9,F- for anyone convicted of any sexual
OL,10,Foffence.
OL,12,FVictim survivors we spoke to say it
OL,13,Fwould provide peace of mind, it would
OL,14,Favoid social media lists, populated by
OL,15,Frumour and it would be a powerful
OL,16,Fdeterrent.
