OL,7,FHowever, there are concerns it would
OL,8,Fincrease vigilantism and essentially
OL,9,Fcut people out of society or push
OL,10,Fcriminal problems to other
OL,11,Fjurisdictions.
OL,13,FA fully public register is very rare,
OL,14,Fand while Guernsey does not have
OL,15,FSarah's Law, if a risk has been
OL,16,Fidentified, the police will sometimes
OL,17,Fgive information to third parties.
OL,19,FITV Channel News has approached Home
OL,20,FAffairs for comment but we have not
OL,21,Freceived a response.
